{"tid":527590,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣東話評述】Six Invitational - APAC Qualifier Day 1","createTime":"2018-01-12T22:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T10:46:59.000Z","uid":35990,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed6f0a61671f1a1ed40e7a102827850845118da","tid":527590,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/061748_58618576e87616878ed5a7e61be9e870.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F061748_58618576e87616878ed5a7e61be9e870.jpeg&h=afe7857d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟自APAC下四個分區，分別係東南亞、日本、韓國同澳洲（及紐西蘭）嘅頂尖隊伍，將會喺呢個比賽度爭奪進入Six Invitational嘅資格。<br />\n<br />\n因為個比賽就喺澳洲度打，要就返佢地個時區，所以我地喺朝早六點半就會開台同大家一齊睇比賽。今次搵咗唯一香港Pro League隊伍 - UniqueMonster嘅Oba同ChangTong幫我地分析下賽事，希望大家多多支持，嚟睇下比賽捧下場！<br />\n<br />\n除咗會喺我自己DevilsGamingHK個Twitch台度開台之外，仲會喺Ubisoft個YouTube Channel度直播，跪求幫手Share<br />\n<br />\nTwitch: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/devilsgaminghk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fdevilsgaminghk%2F&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=001411c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/devilsgaminghk/</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/UbisoftSEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2FUbisoftSEA&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=db4adcc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/UbisoftSEA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/061858_cce52419d4e7c4c2be63e8bbc4c5358c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F061858_cce52419d4e7c4c2be63e8bbc4c5358c.png&h=63c76c5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecb84dfec0806b49d642eeb3062e6be185e262d7","tid":527590,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:44:1